### ==========================================
### 知识库模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：资质库列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/qualifications?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：创建资质
POST http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/qualifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "API测试资质-{{$randomInt 1 9999}}",
  "certificateNo": "API-{{$randomInt 1000 9999}}",
  "issuer": "测试发证机关",
  "holderName": "测试持有人",
  "expiryDate": "2027-12-31",
  "status": "valid"
}

@qualId = 1

### 3. 正常流程：资质详情
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/qualifications/{{qualId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 边界：不存在资质
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/qualifications/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 正常流程：案例库列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/cases?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 正常流程：创建案例
POST http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "API测试案例-{{$randomInt 1 9999}}",
  "industry": "INDUSTRY",
  "outcome": "WON",
  "amount": 100,
  "projectDate": "2026-01-01",
  "description": "通过API创建的测试案例",
  "customerName": "API测试客户",
  "tags": ["API测试"],
  "highlights": ["自动化验证"]
}

@caseId = 1

### 7. 正常流程：案例详情
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/cases/{{caseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 正常流程：案例搜索
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/cases?keyword=测试&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 正常流程：案例引用列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/cases/{{caseId}}/references
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. 正常流程：档案台账
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/archive?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. 边界：空搜索结果
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/cases?keyword=__nonexistent_case_xyz__
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
